#Fine dining in Larkhollow
Despite the size and location, Larkhollow is suprisingly known for its wonderful taste in flavors and food.
-**The Larkhollow tide** - A dive bar where you will meet a handful of locals and try all of our famous "Larkhollow" foods.
-**The Landing** - A staple restaurant right on the harbor with wonderful seafood options and more.
-**Barnacle Tavern** - Also a known one for ther fantastic seafood, has been in our town for almost 60 years.
-**The Ocean Star Market** - Has all of your essential needs with a few homemade pasteries and goodies that are priceless